Wednesday 28 November 2001 19.00 EST First published on Wednesday 28 November 2001 19.00 EST. Tom Shippey is the author of JRR Tolkien: Author of the Century, a companion to Tolkien's work and a spirited defence of fantasy writing, which puts Tolkien in the context of the legendary storytelling tradition. Buy JRR Tolkien: Author of the Century at Amazon.co.uk. Tolkien's fame rests on The Hobbit and The Lord of the Rings.
